[[!tag type/fun]]
[[!tag type/date]]
[[!tag type/chrome]]

Enables use of Discordian dates. `--timeformat` can be used to change
the date format; see `ddate(1)`.

This plugin requires the [[!cpan DateTime]] and 
[[!cpan DateTime::Calendar::Discordian]] perl modules.
